{"tid":1445503,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"記者朋友，聽日黑警記招唔好放過班狗！","createTime":"2019-08-11T14:18:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-11T14:42:12.000Z","uid":262035,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"50801407774999838df29d8646bc9e6f3186b7b8","tid":1445503,"uid":262035,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:18:53.000Z","msg":"用布袋彈射眼嚴重啲定鐳射筆嚴重啲？個女仔隻眼俾狗射到爆撚左，班狗對狗眼爆左未？<br />\n<br />\n你班狗自編自導扮示威者，究竟派左幾多人去燒警署吖？<br />\n<br />\n班狗係葵芳站入面肆意射催淚彈，係咪只要班狗執法就打橫行都得吖？幾時炒撚左係地鐵站射彈班狗同斷佢地長糧？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以牙還牙<br />\n以眼還眼</span></span>"},{"pid":"03d32a008c8922eaeb1ec9ae70c5abef6bcf8258","tid":1445503,"uid":33543,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:19:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/MQZURP7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FMQZURP7.jpg&h=e8ff53ea&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BvexDu8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBvexDu8.jpg&h=6025e5fb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/cnQpuBP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FcnQpuBP.jpg&h=bdc91acf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Product should only be used outdoors</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">記者會上話會跟足廠商指引而無必要親身試彈，宜家冇跟指引就有必要親身試啦？</span><br />\n<br />\n間廠叫NonLethal Technology, 有冇人去提醒下間廠再培訓垃圾狗<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nonlethaltechnologies.com/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nonlethaltechnologies.com%2F&d=5YfG332q5u5uc%2FC0Cq16RWWYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=64eab9a0\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nonlethaltechnologies.com/</a>"},{"pid":"4f2b78480bb7a6a98e3fe3c27ca046f2e66d6bcb","tid":1445503,"uid":13412,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-11T14:20:17.000Z","msg":"其實真係可以係